OL,3,CFermanagh woman talks about hospital
OL,4,Cpressures after early discharge
OL,6,FA woman from Co Fermanagh has told UTV
OL,7,Fshe feels lucky to have escaped a life
OL,8,Fchanging injury after being discharged
OL,9,Ffrom Altnagelvin Hospital only to be
OL,10,Frushed back days later for emergency
OL,11,Fsurgery.
OL,13,FJenny Beattie believes she was sent
OL,14,Fhome too early because the hospital
OL,15,Fneeded the bed.
OL,17,FEmergency general surgery was
OL,18,Ftemporarily suspended at the South
OL,19,FWest Acute Hospital (SWAH) in 2022
OL,20,Fwith patients now transferred two
OL,21,Fhours away for treatment.
