OL,3,CFermanagh woman talks about hospital
OL,4,Cpressures after early discharge
OL,6,FJenny is still recovering from an
OL,7,Femergency procedure last September.
OL,9,FThe 61-year-old from Springfield was
OL,10,Frushed to Altnagelvin Hospital in
OL,11,FLondonderry with severe abdominal pain.
OL,13,F"I was very, very scared. I was
OL,14,Ffrightened because I didn't know what
OL,15,Fwas wrong with me.
OL,17,F"I think it was the fact that you knew
OL,18,Fthat, no matter what, you were two
OL,19,Fhours from the hospital.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
