OL,3,CFermanagh woman talks about hospital
OL,4,Cpressures after early discharge
OL,6,F"A&E was packed with people. The staff
OL,7,Fwere run off their feet. It was unreal.
OL,9,F"I don't know how anybody can cope
OL,10,Fwith that. My heart went out to the
OL,11,Fstaff", she said.
OL,13,FJenny was initially treated and
OL,14,Fdischarged. She feels that she was
OL,15,Fsent home too early because they were
OL,16,Fdesperate for beds.
OL,18,F"I don't think that Altnagelvin is
OL,19,Fcoping. They have all the patients
OL,20,Ffrom Fermanagh.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
