OL,3,CFermanagh woman talks about hospital
OL,4,Cpressures after early discharge
OL,6,F"I have experienced it in the ward
OL,7,Fthat I went into, it was all Fermanagh
OL,8,Fpatients.
OL,10,F"Even the staff themselves said to me
OL,11,Fthat they are overrun because of so
OL,12,Fmany patients coming from Fermanagh",
OL,13,Fshe explained.
OL,15,FBoth Altnagelvin and SWAH are working
OL,16,Funder extreme pressure, like many
OL,17,Fhospitals across Northern Ireland.
OL,19,FThe Trust have appealed to family
OL,20,Fmembers to help with the discharging
OL,21,Fof patients.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
