OL,4,Cpressures after early discharge
OL,6,FJenny's husband collected her and she
OL,7,Fdescribed the journey home as
OL,8,F'horrendous'.
OL,10,F"I asked my husband at one stage to
OL,11,Fpull in and call an ambulance because
OL,12,FI couldn't stick the pain," she said.
OL,14,FIn a matter of days, the Mum of three
OL,15,Fwas rushed to Londonderry because she
OL,16,Fneeded emergency surgery which cannot
OL,17,Fbe performed in Enniskillen as the
OL,18,Fservice was temporarily removed in
OL,19,F2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
