OL,3,CFermanagh woman talks about hospital
OL,4,Cpressures after early discharge
OL,6,F"The surgeon told me the next day he
OL,7,Fsaid, 'You were half an hour from
OL,8,Fperforation and that can be life
OL,9,Fthreatening'.
OL,11,F"It could have been life changing, I
OL,12,Fcould've ended up with a stoma.
OL,13,FThankfully, I didn't.
OL,15,F"It affected me mentally because I
OL,16,Fstarted to get worried. I had nobody
OL,17,Fto talk to.
