OL,3,CFermanagh woman talks about hospital
OL,4,Cpressures after early discharge
OL,6,F"It was very frustrating to be passing
OL,7,Fthe hospital where you live. Where I
OL,8,Fwould have had family around me, that
OL,9,Fcould have come to visit me.
OL,11,F"My surgeon actually came in on his
OL,12,Fday off to see me. That shouldn't be
OL,13,Fthe way", Jenny said.JThe Trust said
OL,14,Fthe change was an 'emergency measure'
OL,15,Fand a matter of 'public safety'.
OL,17,FAt present, 2.5 patients a day are
OL,18,Ftransferred and the Trust states that
OL,19,Fthose patients experience better
OL,20,Foutcomes.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
