OL,4,Cpressures after early discharge
OL,6,FThey have also warned that it will
OL,7,Ftake significant investment for
OL,8,Femergency surgery to return to SWAH.
OL,10,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for the
OL,11,FTrust said: "This change was an
OL,12,F'Emergency Measure' and a matter of
OL,13,F'Public Safety' due to significant and
OL,14,Fongoing difficulties in recruiting and
OL,15,Fretaining the required consultant
OL,16,Fworkforce.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
