OL,3,CFermanagh woman talks about hospital
OL,4,Cpressures after early discharge
OL,6,F"This position was further influenced
OL,7,Fby the introduction of revised
OL,8,FEmergency General Surgery Safety
OL,9,FStandards by the Department of Health
OL,10,Fin June 2022.
OL,12,F"The Trust is now fully compliant with
OL,13,Fthe revised Emergency General Surgery
OL,14,Fstandards designed to ensure that
OL,15,Fpatients across Northern Ireland
OL,16,Freceive safe, specialist emergency
OL,17,Fsurgical care, regardless of where
OL,18,Fthey live.
